-= Configure =-
 * Usage
    $ ./configure "PERSO_FLAGS += -D[Flags]"

 * Flags
    DEBUG     : Debug mode enabled


-= Makefile Options =-
all	 : Creation of the stripped binary
final	 : The binary is compressed with lzma
	   and a stub was added on its ELF beginning
clean	 : classical cleaner
mrproper : Conchita cleaner !
dist	 : Tarball creation
